The Tropical Dome will be lit Orange to celebrate the 105th anniversary of Zonta International.

Celebrating their 105th year in 2024, Zonta International has more than 1,100 clubs with over 27,000 members in sixty-four countries and is renowned for its strong advocacy of women&rsquo;s rights while using their individual and collective expertise in service to their community. The three core campaign messaging of NO to violence against women, YES to gender equality and NOW to climate change. The Zonta Club of Brisbane East Inc, the local member of Zonta International, focuses on its human rights mission of empowering women, supporting girls and young women with education, clothing and basic health and hygiene products, and promoting the achievements of women in industry including science, aeronautics, technology, and business.

This light up is organised by Brisbane Economic Development Agency and Zonta International.&nbsp;

